Place sound files here (referenced by src/lib/audio/index.ts):

  wheel-spin.mp3       — looping spin sound, ~5 sec
  wheel-stop.mp3       — sharp landing thump
  reveal.mp3           — dramatic reveal sting
  correct.mp3          — positive ding
  wrong.mp3            — buzzer / negative chord
  confetti.mp3         — celebration burst
  mission.mp3          — secret-mission tension cue
  tick.mp3             — countdown tick
  background-loop.mp3  — quiet looping bed

The app handles missing files gracefully (play() rejects, swallowed), so it runs
fine without these. Add real files before going live.
